  "response": "For the ICSE 10th Grade English Language exam on February 29th, here are some likely essay and letter writing topics:\n\nEssay Topics:\n1. Impact of Technology on Modern Life\n2. Importance of Education\n3. Environmental Conservation\n4. Social Media: Boon or Bane\n5. Role of Youth in Nation Building\n6. Discipline and Success\n7. Importance of Sports and Physical Fitness\n8. Gender Equality\n9. Digital Learning\n10. Challenges of Climate Change\n\nLetter Writing Topics:\n1. Complaint Letter\n- To the Municipal Corporation about poor road conditions\n- To the school principal about infrastructure issues\n\n2. Formal Application Letter\n- Applying for a school magazine editor position\n- Requesting permission for a school event\n\n3. Informal Letter\n- Writing to a friend about career aspirations\n- Describing a memorable experience\n- Discussing current challenges in life\n\n4. Inquiry Letter\n- Seeking information about a course\n- Requesting details about a summer workshop\n\n5. Business/Official Letter\n- Writing to a company about a product issue\n- Requesting internship opportunities\n\nPreparation tips:\n- Practice writing within time limits\n- Focus on clear, structured writing\n- Use appropriate language and format\n- Proofread your work",
